","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_4WPR4c","text_fjqthA"],"custom_css":[".section__block.section__block--heading {font-size: 30px; color: #806642;}",".section__block.reading-width p {line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #555;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Grey-Crush--3-Sofa-Bed.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_HMkJgA":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_cpFnFE":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Can you get a sofa bed with storage?","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"text_zXhbPC":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>While most sofa beds prioritise the pull-out mechanism, some <strong>corner sofa beds<\/strong> cleverly use the extended section as an <strong>ottoman storage compartment<\/strong>, perfect for keeping pillows and duvets neatly tucked away.<\/p><p>Looking for a practical solution? <strong>Browse our storage beds<\/strong> for a tidy, space-saving option. <\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_cpFnFE","text_zXhbPC"],"custom_css":[".cc-media-with-text {background: #efefef;}",".section__block.section__block--heading {font-size: 30px; color: #806642;}",".section__block.reading-width p {line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #555;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Grey-Crush-Storage-Sofa.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"right","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"slideshow_pQKBKJ":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"slide_fjxVyx":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image_desktop":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Desktop_-_1_22.png","url":"","overlay_position":"justify-center items-center","overlay_text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":false,"subheading":"","heading":"","heading_color":"#ffffff","heading_size":"h0","heading_h1":false,"text":"","enlarge_text":true,"button_1_label":"","button_1_link":"","button_1_style":"btn btn--primary","button_2_label":"","button_2_link":"","button_2_style":"btn btn--primary","transparent_content_color":"#ffffff","countdown_show":false,"countdown_end_date":"","countdown_end_time":"","countdown_end_text":"","enlarge_end_text":false,"countdown_hide_on_end":false,"use_custom_colors":false,"count_color":"#ffffff","bg_color":"#070707","bg_grad":""}}},"block_order":["slide_fjxVyx"],"settings":{"height_mode":"auto","fixed_height_desktop":600,"fixed_height_mobile":350,"mobile_stacked":false,"nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","pagination_color":"#ffffff","nav_position":"justify-center","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":true,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"white","full_width":true,"tint_color":"#000000","tint_opacity":0,"accessibility_info":"","prevent_animation":true}},"multi_column_PpWxJa":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"column_z4q9Hi":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/head.png","media_scale":100,"heading":"","text":"<h3>Fast Delivery<\/h3><p>Experience the convenience of fast delivery when you shop with us. Our dedication to outstanding customer service guarantees that your bed frame and mattress are promptly handled and brought to you. Embrace the convenience and effectiveness of our swift delivery, bringing comfort and elegance to your home quickly. <\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"column_g77nHR":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Cavill_Grey_Bed_D_2000x_9d0599cb-fc00-4ed9-b972-b540e23b1596.png","media_scale":100,"heading":"","text":"<h3>2 Years Warranty<\/h3><p>At Bedroomking, we stand behind the quality and craftsmanship of our beds, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/all-bed-frames\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/all-bed-frames\">bedframes<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/mattresses\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/mattresses\">mattresses<\/a>. We provide you with a 2-years warranty when you purchase a new product from our range of divans, bed frames, mattresses, TV beds, bedroom furniture and kid’s beds to<br\/>ensure your satisfaction and peace of mind. <\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["column_z4q9Hi","column_g77nHR"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_align":"text-center","button_label":"","button_link":"","layout":"grid","column_size":"medium","column_align":"center","image_ratio":"natural","color_scheme":"1","button_style":"btn btn--secondary"}},"testimonials_Eg3UBP":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_nQ77wR":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>Purchased the upholstered bed recently and it has exceeded my expectations! The sleek design, premium materials, and attention to detail make it a true statement piece in my bedroom. The plush upholstery not only adds a touch of sophistication but also ensures a comfortable and restful night's sleep. Couldn't be happier with my purchase!<\/p>","author":"Ethan Pane","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}},"testimonial_hqYGLB":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>Absolutely in love with my new upholstered bed! The storage compartments are a game-changer, providing a practical solution for keeping my bedroom organized. The tufted headboard adds a touch of elegance and complements the overall stylish design. Highly recommend for anyone looking for a perfect blend of style and<br\/>functionality!<\/p>","author":"Lily Alison","author_info":"Author informatio","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}},"testimonial_U7ePb3":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>My upholstered bed is a dream come true! The plush fabric, sturdy frame, and meticulous craftsmanship make for an absolute comfort haven in my bedroom. The blend of luxury and comfort is unparalleled, and I find myself looking forward to bedtime every night. A perfect addition to my sanctuary!<\/p>","author":"Kelly Afong","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}}},"block_order":["testimonial_nQ77wR","testimonial_hqYGLB","testimonial_U7ePb3"],"custom_css":[".section__header h2 {color: #fff; font-size: 28px;}"],"settings":{"heading":"Customer Reviews","show_quotes":true,"testimonial_size":"h5","text_position":"justify-center","text_align":"text-center justify-center","nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":false,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"2","full_width":true}},"recommendations":{"type":"product-recommendations","settings":{"heading":"You may also like","heading_align":"text-start","layout":"carousel","card_size_mobile":"small","card_size":"small","products_to_show":8}},"faq_N6x7ti":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"question_bmdidX":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"What is an upholstered bed?","text":"<p>An upholstered bed is a type of bed frame that features a padded and fabric-covered headboard, footboard, and often side panels.<\/p>"}},"question_cXpYTw":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"What materials are used in your upholstered beds?","text":"<p>Our upholstered beds are crafted using high-quality materials, including durable hardwood for the frame and premium fabrics for the upholstery. We ensure that all materials used are ethically sourced and built to last.<\/p>"}},"question_d8PA7R":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"How do I care for my upholstered bed?","text":"<p>To maintain the pristine condition of your bed, we recommend regular vacuuming to remove dust and occasional spot cleaning for any spills. Always use a mild fabric cleaner and test on an inconspicuous area first. Avoid exposing the bed to direct sunlight for prolonged periods.<\/p>"}},"question_cagMrW":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Is assembly difficult for upholstered beds?","text":"<p>No, upholstered beds typically come with clear<a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/pages\/bed-assembly-instructions\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/pages\/bed-assembly-instructions\"> assembly instructions<\/a>, and assembly is manageable with basic tools. Some models may also feature easy-to-assemble designs. We also provide assembly option for some little added charges.<\/p>"}},"question_mAzMnW":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Can I purchase an upholstered bed with a mattress included?","text":"<p>Yes, you can select the size and type of mattress from our store. This option provides a hassle-free solution for those looking to upgrade their entire sleep setup.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["question_bmdidX","question_cXpYTw","question_d8PA7R","question_cagMrW","question_mAzMnW"],"settings":{"heading":"Frequently Asked Questions","heading_align":"text-center","color_scheme":"1","full_width":true}},"logo_list_ajPTTD":{"type":"logo-list","blocks":{"logo_zf6D63":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/dividebuy-logo-full-colour-rgb.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_iW4h7E":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Klarna_Payment_Badge_svg.webp","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_zyCYXm":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CP_logo_badge_6328x2204_blackmint_png.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_fMPg6y":{"type":"logo","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Logo_Grape-black.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_9mqmWn":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/shop.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_98PYmR":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Google-Pay-logo.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text"